value.name: Porsche 904 - Wikipedia
value.snippet: The Porsche 904 is an automobile which was produced by Porsche in Germany in 1964 and 1965. It was officially called Porsche Carrera GTS due to the same naming rights problem that required renaming the Porsche 901 to Porsche 911 .

value.name: Area code 904 - Wikipedia
value.snippet: Area code 904 is the telephone area code in use for most of the First Coast (northeast) region of the state of Florida, including all of the metropolitan area of Jacksonville. It includes all of Duval County , St. Johns County , Nassau County , and Baker County , and almost all of Clay County .

value.name: Db2 11 - Codes - SQLCODE -904 - IBM
value.snippet: When reason-code is 00E7000E and resource-type is 00001080, SQLCODE -904 was issued by IBM Db2 Analytics Accelerator for z/OS, and resource-name is message text from the accelerator that indicates the cause of the failure. System action. The SQL statement cannot be processed. If the SQL statement being processed was a cursor FETCH, Db2 closes the cursor.
